│ llvm::LoopVectorizationPlanner::buildVPlansWithVPRecipes(llv │
│ m::ElementCount, llvm::ElementCount): Assertion              │
│ `verifyVPlanIsValid(*Plan) && "VPlan is invalid"' failed.    │
│                                                              │
│ ```                                                          │
│                                                              │
│ From this log, I identified the first transformation point   │
│ as:                                                          │
│                                                              │
│ ```                                                          │
